  </h2>



      <div class="indent ">
          
            <div class="">
            <style type="text/css" media="screen">
.intro p{text-indent:2em;word-break:normal;}
</style>
<div class="intro">
    <p>格伦•贝克，《纽约时报》畅销书作家。美国知名脱口秀The Glenn Beck Program主持人及新闻名嘴。</p></div>

            </div>
      </div>








































  

  
    




  

